import { Box,HStack } from "@chakra-ui/layout"
import { Button,Image } from "@chakra-ui/react"

const NavBar=()=>{
    return (
        <>
        
        <Box width="full" boxShadow="xl" p="6" bg="white" height="75px" >
        <HStack spacing="24px" justifyContent="space-between" alignItems="center"> 
            <Box>
               <Image
                borderRadius="full"
                boxSize="50px"
                src="https://www.clipartmax.com/png/middle/290-2903647_travel-png-images-transparent-free-download-air-travel-logo-png.png"
                alt="Segun Adebayo"
                />
            </Box>
            <Box>
                    <Button colorScheme="teal" variant="outline">
                        Logout
                    </Button>
            </Box>
            
        </HStack>
        </Box>
        
        
        </>
    )
}

export default NavBar
